OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Harold C. Bevis  Executive Vice President and Director, Pierson Industries, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 6 different industries.See Board Relationships57--
Background

		Mr. Harold C. Bevis serves as an Executive Vice President of Pierson Industries, Inc. Mr. Bevis served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of Xerium Technologies, Inc. from August 15, 2012 to April 28, 2017. He served as the Chairman of the Board and Chief Executive Officer of Packaging Solutions Holdings at Jen-Coat, Inc., since 2010. He founded Prolamina Corporation in 1971 and served as its Chief Executive Officer from August 2010 to April 2012. He co-founded ... Packaging Solutions Holdings in 2010. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Pliant, LLC (a/k/a Pliant Corp.), since October 22, 2003. He served as the President of Pliant Packaging of Canada Llc. Mr. Bevis served as an Acting Chief Financial Officer of Pliant Corp., from January 26, 2005 to August 31, 2005 and served as its Principal Accounting Officer. He served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Emerson Telecommunications Products Inc.,(alternate name Emerson Telecommunication Products, LLC) since October 22, 2003. He joined Pliant directly from Emerson Electric, where he served as the President of a group of manufacturing companies for the past five years. He led the sale of this group to Emerson while he served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Jordan Telecommunication Products, Inc. Mr. Bevis served as Senior Vice President and General Manager of General Cable Corporation. He held positions of increasing responsibility with GE, Booz, Allen and Hamilton and General Dynamics, where he began his career as an engineer. He served as Chairman of the Board at Prolamina Corporation from August 2010 to April 2012. He serves as a Director of Pierson Industries, Inc. He has been an Independent Director of Commercial Vehicle Group, Inc. since June 2014. He served as a Director of Xerium Technologies, Inc. from August 15, 2012 to April 28, 2017. He served as a Director of Pliant Corp., and Emerson Telecommunications Products Inc. Mr. Bevis has a BS in Industrial Engineering from Iowa State University in 1983 and an MBA in Marketing from Columbia University in 1988.Read Full Background




