Insider Activity


Individual




Harold C. Bevis



Mr. Harold C. Bevis is Independent Director at Commercial Vehicle Group, Inc. and President, Chief Executive Officer & Director at Xerium Technologies, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Commercial Vehicle Group, Inc. and Xerium Technologies, Inc.
Mr. Bevis was previously employed as Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Prolamina Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Pliant LLC, President-Emerson Telecommunications Products by Emerson Electric Co., Engineer by General Dynamics Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Emerson Telecommunication Products, Inc., a Principal by Booz Allen Hamilton, Inc., a Principal by General Electric Co., a Principal by Graybar Electric Co., Inc., a Principal by The Home Depot, Inc., a Principal by Rexel, Inc., and Senior Vice President & General Manager by General Cable Corp.
He received his undergraduate degree from Iowa State University and an MBA from Columbia University.



